AUTHORS
=======

localed - org.freedesktop.locale1 over plain D-Bus, no systemd
required. Maintained for Slackware and other non-systemd Linux
systems.

Maintainer
----------
Nathaniel Russell <naterussell83@gmail.com>
    Project creator and maintainer. Initial implementation of the
    daemon, D-Bus interface, PolKit policy, meson build, and
    SlackBuild packaging. GitHub: @nater1983

----

If you've contributed to localed and don't see your name here,
please open a pull request adding yourself, or file an issue at
https://github.com/nater1983/localed/issues so this file can be
corrected.
